OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FHeavy
OL,6,Fshowers will clear eastwards during
OL,7,Fthe evening. Mostly dry overnight,
OL,8,Fwith clear spells. However, a few
OL,9,Flight showers remain possible in the
OL,10,Fwest and on higher ground. Staying
OL,11,Fbreezy but mild for most.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSunday:FA damp start for some with
OL,14,Fheavy showers. Showers becoming more
OL,15,Fwidespread through the day, into the
OL,16,Fafternoon, turning heavy over the
OL,17,Fhills later. Rather windy around
OL,18,Fcoastal regions.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
